# Spell Casting — `func_CastSpell` @ `0x0097D7B0`

Main spell dispatch: buff/debuff branch vs spell-id jump table. Entry copies context via `func_CopySpellCastContext` (`0x00988E70`).

## Already-named callees (do not rename)

`func_GetSpellID`, `func_IsSpellBuffOrDebuff`, `func_IsMassSpell`, `func_CheckSpellApplyEffect`, `func_ComputeBouncingSpell`, `func_GetSpellDamage`, `func_CheckIceSpellFreeze`, `func_RezAbilities`, `func_SpellSummonElementals`, `func_SpellConjurePhoenix`, `func_SpellFirewall`, `func_GetDefaultStats`.

