## CombatHero ATB after spell `0x20`

If skill `0x8A` and not `func_IsCastATBResetBlocked`, adds ATB via `SetATB` (`+0x18C`) after `func_ClampFloat`. Related: `func_HeroCastATBReset` @ `0x00BBF610` (not a direct callee).

